snippet.title: Patriot Malayalam Teaser | Mammootty | Mohanlal | Mahesh Narayanan | Anto Joseph
snippet.description:
From Anto Joseph Productions, the banner behind some of the most acclaimed and celebrated films in recent times, and visionary filmmaker Mahesh Narayanan comes the Official Teaser of Patriot.

Featuring an ensemble of legends: Mammootty, Mohanlal, Fahadh Faasil, Kunchacko Boban, Nayanthara, and Revathy.

Watch Hindi Teaser: https://youtu.be/j3iXh5ipGmw
Watch Telugu Teaser: https://youtu.be/kzGyAfEJWt0
Watch Tamil Teaser: https://youtu.be/WfGTzc4TsU4

Written & Directed by : Mahesh Narayanan 
Produced by:  Anto Joseph, K G Anil Kumar
Co Produced by : C R Saleem, Subhash George Manuel
Music & Original Score  : Sushin Shyam 
Teaser music mixed- Abin paul
Director of Photography : Manush Nandan ISC
Executive producers: C V Sarathi, Rajesh krishna
Editing : Mahesh Narayanan, Rahul Radhakrishnan
Production Design : Shajie Naduvil, Jibin Jacob
Audiography: Vishnu Govind
Sync Sound : Vaisakh P 
Production Controller: Dixon Poduthas
Line Producers : Sunil Singh, Niroop Pinto, Justin Boban, Jeswin Boban
Make Up: Ranjith Ambady
Lyrics : Anwar Ali
Stunts : Dhilip Subbarayan
Stunt Silva, Mafia Sasi, Riyas- Habib
Costume Design: Dhanya Balakrishanan
Choreography: Shobi Paulraj 
Vfx:Firefly , Eggwhite , Identvfxlab
Chief Associate Director: Linu Antony
Associate Director: Phantom Praveen
Di Colorist : Ashirwad Hadkar ISC
Titles : Sarathvinu
Subtitles : Vivek Renjit (Break Borders)
Stills: Navin Murali
Publicity Design:Aesthetic Kunjamma
PRO : Vaisakh C Vadakkeveedu

snippet.title: [Hindi] BMSD 2025 | Semi Finals | Day 1
snippet.description:
24 top teams clash in the Semi Finals of BMSD 2025. 12 from the Upper Bracket and 12 from the Quarter Finals. Split into 3 groups through the official group draw, every match is packed with high-level BGMI esports action, strategy, and intense competition. Who will rise and secure a spot in the Grand Finals?

Don’t miss a moment of the action, tune in live and cheer for your favorite teams as they push the limits Beyond Limits!

Group A
Phoenix Esports
Nebula Esports
Hero Xtreme Godlike
Blitz Esports
iQOO SOUL
iQOO 8BIT
OnePlus Cincinnati Kids
Infinix TrueRippers

Group B
Autobotz Esports
WHITE WALKERS
Madkings
Victores Sumus
Team AX
OnePlus K9 Esports
GENESIS ESPORTS 
FS ESPORTS

Group C
OnePlus Gods Reign
mysterious4 Esports
Vasista Esports
META NINZA
Likitha Esports
myG Los Hermanos
iQOO ORANGUTAN
First Curiosity

Map Rotation:
Match 1: Erangel–GROUP–A vs B
Match 2: Miramar–GROUP–A vs B
Match 3: Sanhok–GROUP–A vs B
Match 4: Sanhok–GROUP–B vs C
Match 5: Miramar–GROUP–B vs C
Match 6: Erangel–GROUP–B vs C

#BMSD2025 #BATTLEGROUNDSMOBILEINDIA #KRAFTONINDIAESPORTS #BGMI #bgmishowdown #showdown #bgmishowdown2025 #beyondlimits 

Follow us:
https://www.instagram.com/kraftonindiaesports/
https://www.youtube.com/c/BATTLEGROUNDSMOBILEINDIAEsports
https://x.com/KIEOFFICIAL_

Srinivasa Govinda Tamil Devotional Song on Lord Balaji (Perumal), Sung by Ramu & Composed by Veeramani Kannan, Lyricis by Varasree, Produced by Apoorva Videos. Licensed by Apoorva Audios.

Singari enna konjam 
Sikkama sikkeduthaa 
Kaathoda sutha vecha 
Ringa ringa 

Mannadhi mannarellam 
Pinnadi vandhalumae
Ennanda maatikina 
Thanga thanga 

Kaandhazhi kannuladhan 
Thalladi undhuputtan
Soodana soora bodha 
Yerikicha kicha 

Mellama enna Neeyum 
Thalukka thalli vitta
Thaana Nana Thaana nanaaa

Manama thechu vutten sandhanama 
Yethi vecha kungumamaa 
Paathane kannala 
Ketene unna pola 

Aaki vechu kenjanuma 
Thooki vechu konjanuma 
Manama kekuriye
Pechu nallalla

Sikkama sikkedutha
Kaathoda sutha vecha 
Ringa ringa 

Mannadhi mannarellam 
Pinnadi vandhalumae
Ennanda maatikina 
Thanga thanga

Ayy yedakuda iduppula 
Yekachakka madippula 
Uchakattathuku pona 
Air-u la

Adi medu pallam paathu na 
Sokki pona gar uh la 
Thooki vechu thakka poren
Ner-u la

Mangai aval koondhalukkullae 
Malyutham nadakkudha 
Mandram vandha thendralum ippo 
Vekkapattu sirikkudhaa 
Winter-u la veyilu adikka 
Odambellam Silukkuthaa
Narambellam podachukkunu needhan needhan Venumunu Kizhiliyee

Jannal vazhi minnalum therikkudhu 
Kaalum rendum pinninu kedakkudhu 
Moonu mani mudinchum adhunga konjunu kedakkudhu

snippet.title: Payal Ki Khanak | Official Video | Hindi New Song | Anil Rawat | Mohit Love | Bhaigiri Music
snippet.description:
Payal Ki Khanak | Official Video | Hindi New Song | Anil Rawat | Mohit Love | Bhaigiri Music 

#payalkikhanak 
#पायल_की_खनक
#payal_ki_khanak
#पायल_की_खनक_से_जगेंगे_सजना
#payal_ki_khanak_se_jagege_sajna
#anilrawatkegane 
#anilrawat 
#anil_rawat 
#anilrawatsong
#अनिल_रावत_सोंग
payal ki khanak anil rawat song
पायल की खनक अनिल रावत सोंग
anil rawat viral song
अनिल रावत वायरल सोंग
payal ki khanak viral song



हो कैसे आऊ मिलवे बजेंगे कंगना 
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

हा आवे तो आजा झूठी बात क्यों बनावे,,
दो महीना से रानी येठ क्यों दिखावे 

हा बात बनावे बैठी बैठी अंगना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जावे संजना,,

हा करले सवर बाबू मिलने भी आऊंगी,,
प्यार की है प्यास पानी हाथ से पिलाऊंगी,,

प्यार से बडो कोई रोग हतना,,
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

न चहिए प्यार मोकू बारिश की बूंद को,,
छाती से लगाके देजा मौकु सकून सो,,

हा खून सो जलावे गोरी तेरा हंसना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जाएंगे सजना,,

Ho kese aau milve bajenge kangna,,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna 

Aave to aaja jhuti baat Kyo banave,,
Do mahina se rani yeth kyo dikhave,,
Ha baat banave bethi bethi angana,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna

Ha karle savar babu milne bhi aaungi ,,
Pyar ki hai pyas pani hath se pilaungi,,,
Pyar se bdo koi rog hath na,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna,,

N chahiye pyar moku barish ki bund ko,,
Chhati se lagake deja moku sakun so,,

khoon  so jalave gori tera hasna,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna,,,

Lyrics:-

हो नीली पीली चूड़ी ले अईयो कंगना,,
करवाचौथ पे उपासी रहूंगी सजना,,,

हा लंबे लंबे घूंघट को धीरे से उठईयो 
पतले पतले होटन पे लिपस्टिक लगईयो 

हा सोलह सिंगार गोरी करियो जरूर,,
रे गोरी तोड़ के दिखावे अनिल चांद को गुरूर,,

हो बाबुल की गलियों से तेरे घर आई रे
बैठी हु प्यासी शरम तोय न आई रे,,

पानी तेरे हाथ से पिलादे सजना,,
करवाचौथ पे उपासी रहूंगी सजना,,

हा छोटी छोटी बातन पे रूठो न गोरी,,
आवे में हो गई है थोड़ी सी देरी,,

हा सॉरी सॉरी बोलूं मोकु करियों न दूर,,
रे गोरी तोड़ के दिखावे अनिल चांद को गुरूर,,,


Ho nili pili chudi le aiyo Kangna,,
Karwachauth pe upasi rahungi sajna,,

Ha lambe lambe gungate ko dhire se uthaiyo,,
Patale patale hotan pe lipistic lagaiyo,,

Ha solah singar gori kariya jarur,,
Re gori tod ke dikhave Anil Chand ko gurur,

Ho Babul ki galiyon se tere ghar aai re,,
Bhethi hu pyasi sharam toy na aai re,,

Paani tere haath se pilade sajna,,
Karwachauth pe upasi rahungi sajna,,

Ha chhoti chhoti baatan pe rutho na gori,,
Aave me ho gai hai thodi si deri,,

Re sorry sorry bolu moku Kariyo na door,,
Re gori tod ke dikhave Anil Chand ko gurur,,,

Rendered in the soulful voices of Altamash Faridi, Arijit Singh, Shadab Faridi, and Shreya Ghoshal, this Love Sentimental classic is sure to pull at your heartstrings. Evoking a sense of earnest love and deep emotion, this timeless piece from the 2023ss is a pure treat for all Hindi song lovers.

snippet.title: Afghanistan vs Bangladesh | 2nd T20I | 2025 | Full Match Highlights

The rivalry between Afghanistan and Bangladesh is as close as it gets in T20Is, and it heats up again tonight as a three-match series begins! Afghanistan lead the head-to-head 7-6, and with the T20 World Cup approaching, both teams are desperate to find form.

सुन्दरकांड” – श्री राम चरित मानस का 5 वा अध्याय/कांड है। सुन्दर कांड (Sundar Kand) को सबसे पहले रामायण में श्री वाल्मीकि जी ने संस्कृत में लिखा था। बाद में तुलसी दस जी ने जब श्री राम चरित मानस लिखी, तो सुन्दर कांड का अवधी भाषा वाला रूप हम सब के सामने आया 
सुन्दरकाण्ड में हनुमान जी का सीता माता को खोजने के लिए की गयी लंका यात्रा का सम्पूर्ण मनमोहक बखान किया गया है।
सुन्दरकांड एक ऐसा भाग है जो सिर्फ हनुमान जी की वीरता का बखान करता है । सुन्दर कांड हनुमान जी पर केंद्रित सबसे पुरानी रचना है। ऐसा माना जाता है के सुन्दरकाण्ड के पाठ से सभी मनोकामनाएं पूर्ण होती हैं ।

सुन्दर कांड के फायदे | Benefits of - Sunder Kand
 यह कहा जाता है कि चालीस सप्ताह तक लगातार जो कोई श्रद्धापूर्वक Sundarkand का पाठ करता है, तो उसके सभी मनोरथ पूरे होते हैं तथा जीवन के सभी कष्ट, दुःख, परेशानियाँ दूर हो जाती हैँ । कई ज्योतिषी भी विपरित परिस्थितियों में सुंदरकांड करने की ही सलाह देते हैं। यदि किसी व्यक्ति के जीवन में अत्यधिक परेशानियां हो तथा कोई काम नहीं बन पा रहा है, आत्मविश्वास की कमी हो तो सुंदरकांड के पाठ से शुभ फल प्राप्त होता है।

Set sail on a magical journey of love and emotion with the melodious voices of Shreya Ghoshal and Udit Narayan. Experience the beautiful mix of melodies with this classic Hindi song, 'Woh Humse Khafa Hain' from the movie 'Tumsa Nahin Dekha A Love Story'. This emotion-charged track will transport you back to the 2004s, an era of heart-touching romantic music, melting your heart with every line. 

Poignantly penned and beautifully sung, this lyrical symphony brings to life a heartfelt love story, filled with delicate emotions and deep feelings. So, let the magic of music take over, allow it to evoke emotions and memories of a bygone era filled with love and passion.

Kaise Aaun Milane Bajenge Kangana (official video) Anil Rawat Deva mast | Payal Ki Khanak Se | song

👇👇👇👇👇
Ho kese aau milve bajenge kangna,,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna 

Aave to aaja jhuti baat Kyo banave,,
Do mahina se rani yeth kyo dikhave,,
Ha baat banave bethi bethi angana,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna

Ha karle savar babu milne bhi aaungi ,,
Pyar ki hai pyas pani hath se pilaungi,,,
Pyar se bdo koi rog hath na,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna,,

N chahiye pyar moku barish ki bund ko,,
Chhati se lagake deja moku sakun so,,

khoon  so jalave gori tera hasna,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna,,,

हो कैसे आऊ मिलवे बजेंगे कंगना 
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

हा आवे तो आजा झूठी बात क्यों बनावे,,
दो महीना से रानी येठ क्यों दिखावे 

हा बात बनावे बैठी बैठी अंगना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जावे संजना,,

हा करले सवर बाबू मिलने भी आऊंगी,,
प्यार की है प्यास पानी हाथ से पिलाऊंगी,,

प्यार से बडो कोई रोग हतना,,
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

न चहिए प्यार मोकू बारिश की बूंद को,,
छाती से लगाके देजा मौकु सकून सो,,

हा खून सो जलावे गोरी तेरा हंसना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जाएंगे सजना,,

snippet.title: KAKA New Punjabi Song - Mitti De Tibbe (Official Video) | Afsha Khan | Latest Punjabi Songs 2025
snippet.description:
👉🏻 SUBSCRIBE to Times Music - https://bit.ly/tmchnl

Dive into the emotional world of Mitti De Tibbe, a beautifully written and composed song by KAKA, featuring Afsha Khan. This heartfelt melody touches on love, loss, and the quiet strength of letting go.

Teri khushboo ch teri mitti di mahek main mehsoos karda aan, uss Mitti Di Khushboo ch main tenu yaad karda aan. Chheti mil Chheti  Mil.
Witness a beautiful love story unfold with this new Punjabi song

ਤੇਰੀ ਖੁਸ਼ਬੂ ਚ ਤੇਰੀ ਮਿੱਟੀ ਦੀ ਮਹਿਕ ਮੇਂ ਮਹਿਸੂਸ ਕਰਦਾ ਆਂ, ਉਸ ਮਿੱਟੀ ਦੀ ਖੁਸ਼ਬੂ ਚ ਮੈਂ ਤੇਨੂ ਯਾਦ ਕਰਦਾ ਆ। ਛੇਤੀ ਮਿਲ, ਛੇਤੀ ਮਿਲ।
ਕਾਕਾ ਜੀ-ਮਿੱਟੀ ਦੇ ਟਿੱਬੇ ਦੇ ਇਸ ਨਵੇਂ ਪੰਜਾਬੀ ਗੀਤ, 2022 ਦੇ ਨਾਲ ਇੱਕ ਖੂਬਸੂਰਤ ਪ੍ਰੇਮ ਕਹਾਣੀ ਸਾਹਮਣੇ ਆਈਏ।

Tērī khuśabū ca tērī miṭī dī mahika mēṁ mahisūsa karadā āṁ, usa miṭī dī khuśabū ca maiṁ tēnū yāda karadā ā. Chētī mila, chētī mila.
Kākā jī-miṭī dē ṭibē dē isa navēṁ pajābī gīta, 2025 dē nāla ika khūbasūrata prēma

Lyrics: 
Mitti De Tibbe De Sajje Paase, Tobhe De Naalo Naal Ni 
Vich Charanda De Bheda Jo Chaare, Baabe Ton Puchhi Mera Haal Ni
Sadak Vallin Tere Kamre Di Khidki Di, Takhti Te Likhya E Naa Mera
Ghodi Vechi Jithe Chache Tere Ne, Ohi E Jaane Gran Mera

Tu mere raste nu takdi hi reh gyi, Ubbal ke chah teri chulleh ch pai gyi
Mera pata teri saheli nu pata e, Tun tan kamlie ni jakdi hi reh gyi
Karkhane vaale modd de kole, Taanga udeeken tu bohd de kole
Aaja kade meri ghodi te beh ja, Pyar naal gal pyar di keh ja
Neend te chain ta pehla hi tu lae gyi, Jaan hi rehndi e ah v  tu laija

Akhan vicho kinna boldi ain, Chehre mere cho ki tohl di ain
Mere vicho tenu esa ki dikheya ke baaki enne dil rol di ain 
Balan leauni e jungle cho aathan nu, Naal pakki ik rakhdi ain sathan nu
Kikkar di tahni nu maan jeha hunda e, Moti danda naal choohni ain daatan nu

Lakk tere utte jachde bade, Nehro 2 bhardi pittal de ghade
Shehro pata krke sehre di keemat, Tere piche kinne firde chhade 
Tu taan chaubare cho parda hataake, Chori chori mainu dekhdi ain 
Yaar mittar ik mere da kehna ain, Naina naal dil chekdi ain

Agle maheene mandir te mela e, Mele de din tera yaar vi vehla e
Gaani nishani tenu laike deni e, Alle palle mere chaar ku dhela e
Der kyon launi e jugat ladaa lai, Mainu sabar ni tu kahli machaa le
Bhua ja maasi jaa chachi nu kehke, Ghar tere meri tu gall chala lai

Lipp ke ghar sadda nanad teri ne, Kandh utte tera chehra banaata
Chehre de naal koi kaala jeha waah ke, Ohde mathe utte sehra sajaata
Pata lagga tenu shonk phullan da, Phullan da raja gulaab hi e
Chaar beeghe vich khushbu ugauni, Hale Kake da khwaab hi e
Doulaan te ghumdi de saaha ch ghul ke, Khushboaan khush honn giya
Udd da dupatta dekh ke tera, Koylaan vi gaane gaun gia

Mitti De Tibbe De Sajje Paase, Tobhe De Naalo Naal Ni 
Vich Charanda De Bheda Jo Chaare, Baabe Ton Puchhi Mera Haal Ni
Sadak Vallin Tere Kamre Di Khidki Di, Takhti Te Likhya E Naa Mera
Ghodi Vechi Jithe Chache Tere Ne, Ohi E Jaane Gran Mera

Tu mere raste nu takdi hi reh gyi, Ubbal ke chah teri chulleh ch pai gyi
Mera pata teri saheli nu pata e, Tun tan kamlie ni jakdi hi reh gyi
Karkhane vaale modd de kole, Taanga udeeken tu bohd de kole
Aaja kade meri ghodi te beh ja, Pyar naal gal pyar di keh ja
Neend te chain ta pehla hi tu lae gyi, Jaan hi rehndi e ah v  tu laija

Akhan vicho kinna boldi ain, Chehre mere cho ki tohl di ain
Mere vicho tenu esa ki dikheya ke baaki enne dil rol di ain 
Balan leauni e jungle cho aathan nu, Naal pakki ik rakhdi ain sathan nu
Kikkar di tahni nu maan jeha hunda e, Moti danda naal choohni ain daatan nu

Lakk tere utte jachde bade, Nehro 2 bhardi pittal de ghade
Shehro pata krke sehre di keemat, Tere piche kinne firde chhade 
Tu taan chaubare cho parda hataake, Chori chori mainu dekhdi ain 
Yaar mittar ik mere da kehna ain, Naina naal dil chekdi ain

Agle maheene mandir te mela e, Mele de din tera yaar vi vehla e
Gaani nishani tenu laike deni e, Alle palle mere chaar ku dhela e
Der kyon launi e jugat ladaa lai, Mainu sabar ni tu kahli machaa le
Bhua ja maasi jaa chachi nu kehke, Ghar tere meri tu gall chala lai

Lipp ke ghar sadda nanad teri ne, Kandh utte tera chehra banaata
Chehre de naal koi kaala jeha waah ke, Ohde mathe utte sehra sajaata
Pata lagga tenu shonk phullan da, Phullan da raja gulaab hi e
Chaar beeghe vich khushbu ugauni, Hale Kake da khwaab hi e
Doulaan te ghumdi de saaha ch ghul ke, Khushboaan khush honn giya
Udd da dupatta dekh ke tera, Koylaan vi gaane gaun gia

snippet.description:
Immerse yourself in the heartfelt world of Bollywood's sentimental classics. Lend your ears to 'Yeh Reshmi Zulfen (Revival)', a quintessential melody from 1969, beautifully rendered by the legendary Mohammed Rafi. This song remains a testament to the honey-filled tones, soul-stirring lyrics, and the deeply emotional delivery that defined his style. The melodic journey takes you back to the iconic Bollywood of the 1969s, a golden period filled with poetic compositions and passionate performances. 

Allow the magic of Mohammed Rafi's voice to fill your hearts in this revival of 'Yeh Reshmi Zulfen' from the album 'Revival Vol.13'. Dive deep into nostalgia and experience the timeless appeal of the Hindi film industry's most loved sentimental songs.

snippet.description:
Majhi Re | Zubeen Garg | Lyrical Video | cover by Basudeb Rajbanshi |Tribute to Jubin Garg 
💔 আজ আমাদের মাঝে নেই কিংবদন্তি কণ্ঠশিল্পী জুবিন গার্গ দা।

snippet.description:
Madam Ji (Official Video) Masoom Sharma | Amar Karnawal, Pinna Music | New Haryanvi Song 2025 
  
#madamji #masoomsharma #amarkarnawal #pinnamusic #newharyanvisong2025 #newharyanvisongs2025 #haryanvisongs2025 #haryanvisongs #haryanvisong 

Title : Madam Ji
Singer / Composer - Masoom Sharma 
Female Singer - Rekha Goswami
Music - Pinna Music
Lyrics - Amar Karnawal
Project By : Vikas Rajana

Label : @masoomsharma

SUBSCRIBE : https://www.youtube.com/@MasoomSharma

Contact For More Information
► FACEBOOK :   / iammasoomsharma  
► INSTAGRAM : https://bit.ly/3g8Haln

Distribution Partner : Ziaan Entertainment FZCO

Lyrics :
Ho Tu Kyun Rakhta Hai Bin Baat Mein
Itna Asla Apne Sath Mein
Saiyan Tu To Superstar Tha
Ban Gaya Kya Tu Raaton Raat Mein
Hath Mein Asla Gaat Mein Jaan
Minute Mein Khada Khinda Dyan Saang
Karya Koi Maada Na Pareshan
Re Dushman Ke Banwadya Than
Baje 47 Ke Fire, Raat Ne Gunje Shehar
Je Hoja Mahra Kise Te Bair
Fer Ude Manas Marte Hain
Re Hum To Gunde Hain Madam Ji, Gundagardi Karte Hain
Vahan Tera Shehar Thehar Jata Hai Jahan Se Hum Guzarte Hain

Ho Raakhe Tu Balam Gaadi Kaali
Diggi Mein Rakha 47
Bole Koye Tere Te Aadha
Uske Munh Pe Laade Taali
Mhari Dhaak Chale Se Thaddi
Raat Ne Piven Hath Ki Kaadi
Rakhu Automatic Asla
Madam Automatic Gaadi
 Baddi Soch Approach Sifarish
Ghar Ka Iklota Vaaris
Hoja Ek Phone Pe Baarish
Khulle Round Baraste Hain
Re Hum To Gunde Hain Madam Ji, Gundagardi Karte Hain
Vahan Tera Shehar Thehar Jata Hai Jahan Se Hum Guzarte Hain

Manne Tere Kaale Kaam Na Bhaate
Yaar Tere Bank Mein 15 Khaate
Rapiye Ginti Mein Aate
Log Ke Kare Samajh Ni Paate
Re Dhandhe Gorya Mein Karu Kale
Asle Rakhu Russia Aale
Sheikha Gelyan Gadhi Yaari
Paadu Baith Dubai Mein Chaale
Re Tera Karnawaliya Pakka Paapi
Amar Bas Eke Naam Se Kaafi
Darshan Honde Koni Baaki
Milan Ne Log Taraste Hain
Re Hum To Gunde Hain Madam Ji, Gundagardi Karte Hain
Vahan Tera Shehar Thehar Jata Hai Jahan Se Hum Guzarte Hain

Humare Avm Gana Channel mein Chhatishgarhi Hits Gana aap logo ke liye prastut karte hain. Hum Chahte hain ki har baar aapke pasand ka New Cg Song aap logo ko de. 
Hume apne comment me bataye Chhattisgarhi Geet kisake aawaz me sunana chahte avam video dekhana chahte hain. Hum Humare gana ko Dj Version mein bhi layenge, hum humare Avm Gana Me hit chhattisgarhi gana dene ke liye pratibaddh hain. 
Hum humare Chhattisgarhi geet ko badhava dene wale singer & actor Tijan bai, Usha Barle, Mamta Chandrakar, Anuj sharma, Nitin Dubey, Dilip shadangi, Alka Chandrakar, chaya Chandrakar, Bhupendra sahu, Mithilesh sahu, Kuleshwar tamrakar , Kavita Vaishanvi, Sunil Soni,
Kanchan joshi, Sarla Gandharw, Anupma mishra, Sunny pandey, Dilip Ray, Shashi Rangila, Virendra Chaturvedi, Shyam Kuteliya, Karan Chauhan, Kiran Chauhan, Monika Verma, Seema Kaushik, Gorelal Barman, Garima Diwakar, Dilip Lahariya, Devesh Dahariya
Mann Quereshi, Anikriti Chauhan, Amlesh Nagesh, isi tarah chhattisgarh ke hum sabhi any singer avam actor ko tahe dil se Dhanywaad Karte hain. Jo Humari Chhattisgarhi Boli ko Desh va Videsh me Badhava De Rahe Hain...

snippet.title: Chal Kahin Door Nikal Jayen  |  Doosara Aadmi  |  Kishore Kumar  |  Lata Mangeshkar
snippet.description:
Step back in time and revisit the classic love anthems of the 1977s. This musical journey highlights the golden era of Hindi cinema with unique renditions by the legends Kishore Kumar, Lata Mangeshkar, and Mohammed Rafi. In focus, 'Chal Kahin Door Nikal Jayen' from 'Doosara Aadmi' is a song that perfectly captures the essence of Love and Romance. Let's relive those times and immerse ourselves in the magical melodies of yesteryears.

Chapter list:
Chal Kahin Door Nikal Jayen

Song Credits:


Credits :

Song: Chal Kahin Door Nikal Jayen
Album: Doosara Aadmi
Artist: Kishore Kumar | Lata Mangeshkar | Mohammed Rafi
Music Director: Rajesh Roshan
Lyricist: Majrooh Sultanpuri 


Leave your heart behind and dive into this beautiful world of love and music. Don't forget to like this video, comment your favorite song from this collection, and subscribe to our channel for more musical gems. As we close, remember to keep the love for music alive as we say, 'Let the magic of music live on...'
